WEBVTT

00:00:13.033 --> 00:00:18.706 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Dandelions growing
on top of the hill,

00:00:18.706 --> 00:00:23.627 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Mountains in the distance,
wind blowing through the field,

00:00:23.627 --> 00:00:29.425 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Warmth of the sun
casting down from the sky,

00:00:29.425 --> 00:00:34.513 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Birds fly up above,
Clouds rolling by—

00:00:34.513 --> 00:00:40.060 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What did I do
To see such beauty?

00:00:40.060 --> 00:00:45.858 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And what do I do
To show how much I care?

00:00:45.858 --> 00:00:51.822 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ve got to be thankful,
Tell Jehovah in prayer

00:00:51.822 --> 00:00:57.494 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That I’m thankful
For the love that he shares.

00:00:57.494 --> 00:01:00.456 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Stop, 
look around,

00:01:00.456 --> 00:01:05.252 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Take a moment,
and let it sink down in my heart.

00:01:05.252 --> 00:01:10.507 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Never take for granted
all he’s done.

00:01:10.507 --> 00:01:20.809 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ve got to be thankful.
